{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"4fe74ae37c","title":"对地方党委领导新闻事业的指示","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"7cd81f9e0d","index":0,"year":1958,"month":null,"day":null,"articleId":"4fe74ae37c"}],"tags":[{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"c20d333791","name":"关键人物文稿","type":"文稿大类"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji41","name":"毛泽东全集第41卷","internal":false,"official":true,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/41-OCR.pdf"},{"id":"wansui4","name":"毛泽东思想万岁(1958-1960卷)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"未知","files":"/books/wansui4a.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji41":{"comments":[{"id":"3aa17b0df3","publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"4fe74ae37c","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"1958年，新华社国内分社和人民日报记者站合并。这是毛泽东在听取关于此事汇报时，对地方党委领导新闻事业的指示。"}],"contents":[{"id":"0fe3ef45a5","type":"title","text":"对地方党委领导新闻事业的指示","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"4fe74ae37c"},{"id":"3aa17b0df3","type":"paragraph","text":"早就应该这样做，过去（分社）省也管不了，现在这个办法是适应国家的情况的。省委管比你们有办法，分社也就不孤单了，就有依靠了。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"4fe74ae37c"}],"page":{"id":"b9e203982f","publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"4fe74ae37c","start":156,"end":156}},"wansui4":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"36d5ed103a","type":"paragraph","text":"一九五八年。新华社国内分社和人民日报记者站合并，体制下放给地方党委。曾向主席汇报此事，主席说：","index":1,"publicationId":"wansui4","articleId":"4fe74ae37c"},{"id":"544655dd04","type":"title","text":"对地方党委领导新闻事业的指示","index":0,"publicationId":"wansui4","articleId":"4fe74ae37c"},{"id":"9cd093ba1b","type":"paragraph","text":"早就应该这样做，过去（分社）省也管不了，现在这个办法是适应国家的情况的。省委管比你们有办法。分社也就不孤单了。就有依靠了。","index":2,"publicationId":"wansui4","articleId":"4fe74ae37c"}],"page":{"id":"76eb61f87a","publicationId":"wansui4","articleId":"4fe74ae37c","start":374,"end":374}}}},"__N_SSG":true}